    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, it runs well but may require some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak shape. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone looking for a budget-friendly option without expecting a showroom finish.",
