    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, a testament to consistent maintenance and mechanical integrity. This specimen offers a refined driving experience, characterized by smooth power delivery and a well-preserved interior. Thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards for safety and performance, this motorcar represents an exceptional acquisition for the professional seeking a reliable and sophisticated transport solution. We invite serious inquiries to experience its superior handling and enduring quality firsthand.",
      "price": 36450.0,
